MainActivity.kt - activity_main.xml // this is used to contain the Fragments
HomeFragment.kt - fragment_home.xml // contains the main initial screen (what used to be activity_main.xml)
BeeListRecyclerViewAdapter.kt
BeeListRecyclerViewItem.kt - bee_list_recycler_view_item.xml   
MapFragment.kt - fragment_map.xml 
CameraActivity.kt - fragment_camera.xml

Main -> Camera (picture data) -> Camera confirm (picture data)
Camera (could get location data, bundle with picture + Date()), send to Firebase -> Map Fragment

Map Activity (recalling all data on firebase) -> Add bee, or return. 
 (if back button is pressed, go to MainActivity only)

https://developer.android.com/reference/android/content/SharedPreferences
